Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:33.98,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H006229&}Boss Fight\N~The Final Light~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:39.80,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll be able to hit \Nyou with everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.93,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,My powers... and my rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.63,sign_3476_43_3_Years_Ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0B09D7&}Output 20%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.80,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.82,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,This is finally getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:20.99,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.17,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You're enjoying this too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:29.50,Main,Koyama,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.90,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting in\Na whole different stratosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:40.55,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,As righteous as you try to sound,\Ndeep down, you're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.57,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:48.81,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to be released\Nfrom your shackles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.52,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,We are freer than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.37,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.84,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,How... How could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.83,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be so foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:23.44,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It may have only been for a moment, \Nbut I let this power control me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.31,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You're so emotionally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:33.75,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll never catch up to me,\Nno matter how far you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.91,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I am the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:41.86,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,How did your life end up being so hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:46.34,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I can't judge you for the life\Nyou chose, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.84,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You were just unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.92,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:56.34,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one in this world \Nthat is as lucky as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.80,sign_3476_43_3_Years_Ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0B09D7&}Output 50%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.51,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven bestowed these powers upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:06.20,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,and made you all extras,\Ncreated solely to make my star shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.06,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then it wasn't luck \Nthat you were lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.58,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It was bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.73,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.69,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only one\Nwho existed in your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.29,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You lived in overwhelming solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.18,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I know that feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.47,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Living in a world where I'm completely alone,\None I want to forget forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.60,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.61,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.45,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.21,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You might not believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.92,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,but I really don't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.32,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.09,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.71,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.79,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,The president's aura is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.27,Main,Saku,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean it's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.90,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.53,Main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. Is that boy actually human?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.93,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a normal middle school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.32,Italics,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san... You used a tremendous \Namount of power again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:35.77,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:39.20,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's aura didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.02,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,It changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:48.08,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,My dad mentioned before that \Nhe picked up the habit of only awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.92,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,when put under a lot of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.23,Main,Tsuchiya,0000,0000,0000,,This goes beyond human understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.70,Main,Muraki,0000,0000,0000,,How can one man's powers be so immense?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:32.16,Italics,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeo... This is the one day in your life\Nyou shouldn't try to do the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:36.45,Italics,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,He's already using way more power\Nthan he did when beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.95,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't win, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.63,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You're not responsible for any of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.08,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.97,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.07,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.31,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm going to let you say\Nyou're done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:59.04,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.09,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.06,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,As much as I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.45,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:09.28,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the power to show you a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:15.71,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You awakened my destructive impulses,\Nnow you have to deal with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.17,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go hiding in your shell now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.68,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:32.67,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that you could turn over a new leaf\Nand become a better person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.46,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,but that hope's gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.66,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I-It appears... that we're both...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:47.23,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,influencing each other quite a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:51.56,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But I couldn't be a good influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.45,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done. We can both lose at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.62,sign_3476_43_3_Years_Ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0D09D7&}Output 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.63,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.71,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I might actually die...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:09.05,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.01,Flashback,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.11,Flashback,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:14.84,Flashback,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.30,Flashback,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.64,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.50,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing compared to the fear\Nof losing all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:42.71,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Body improvement! Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.20,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.83,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,If something like that makes it outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.83,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It'll explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.76,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It'll explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.31,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:41.07,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Run away! Everyone, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:41.96,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.14,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.80,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He ended up releasing too much \Nenergy and self-destructed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.42,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You're bleeding like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.65,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.48,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is an \Nexcessive amount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.54,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure an explosion will happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.11,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,a huge one at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.04,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying we won't \Nbe able to contain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.12,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.48,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.60,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run. We're gonna get caught \Nup in that if we stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.74,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,That's the president's final light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.31,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Our president who was trying \Nto take over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.84,Main,Hatori,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and run! You're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.50,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, where's Shigeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.34,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You made the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.96,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to avoid this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.36,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Your only choice is to end my life—\Nto sever the energy source—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.80,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,before the explosion happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.11,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.65,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to contain the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.82,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you aren't able to defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:47.79,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,save your friends, or save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:51.75,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,With your powers, you should've \Nbeen able to handle this better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:55.00,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Just having powers doesn't mean\Neverything works out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.64,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,But that's perfectly fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:02.48,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you make\Nthe important choices yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:06.43,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the protagonist of my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.44,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I chose to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:15.39,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I dislike you, \Nto leave you to suffer on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.06,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,would just be too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.13,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.05,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with that filthy cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:30.52,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the poor thing was drenched \Nand shivering in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.12,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,And think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.34,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Sho will grow up into a gentle boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.30,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to grow up watching you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.98,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be gentle. Gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.18,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to be so violent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:50.02,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,To lead an organization,\NI need to establish my dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.73,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,You can't move people's hearts \Nwith psychic powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.36,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,No, power is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:59.32,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have this power, \Npeople will follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:02.10,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's true for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.03,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:06.45,Flashback,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Sho is also showing interest \Nin my powers as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.53,Flashback,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.22,Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,When did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.94,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,If I can absorb it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.47,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. You'll just end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.78,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to apologize, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:34.24,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Then you need to do it say it loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:41.01,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:45.94,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I also have someone I need \Nto express my feelings to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.66,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.94,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx60\fscy200\pos(320,10)\c&H59FFF7&}Mob Psycho
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.44,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx60\fscy200\pos(320,10)\c&H59FFF7&\clip(m 199 12 l 434 12 435 50 398 50 395 44 391 42 390 35 389 29 392 24 392 20 386 22 380 26 380 32 380 36 375 39 371 43 370 46 371 63 202 64)}Mob Psycho
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.22,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.91,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.62,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.45,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.57,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.68,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.49,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,He's regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.23,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.79,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.36,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:43.37,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we should get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.21,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.01,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:49.82,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,All of our wounds have been healed. \NOur clothes are in shambles, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.43,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.53,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeo, what's up with\Nthe left side of your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.88,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the bold fashion statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:02.54,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... You never cease to amaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.57,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,I do consider you my rival, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.14,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wander off too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.58,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,This ground... It's not concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.80,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,My mind feels all spacey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.96,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,The sky seems cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.93,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.60,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,There's the exit. Watch out for \Nthings that may fall onto your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.01,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.93,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly, there aren't any \Nnews helicopters flying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.38,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.23,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,They're too scared to come here\Nwhen they know so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.77,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Everything seems fine, \Neven after that giant explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:39.98,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously thought\Nyou were a goner back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:48.57,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure ground zero\Nwould've been eviscerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.79,Flashback,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:55.37,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But what appeared there happened to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:56.77,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.04,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:01.82,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?\NAre you still actually hurt somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:05.50,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ritsu. I think my body's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.57,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, whenever I use a lot of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.07,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hard time staying awake afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:11.87,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.89,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry you partway,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.28,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,so you can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.19,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Carry him where? Our house is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:28.50,Flashback,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, he'll fix up your house, \Nbut he'll need three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.24,Flashback,Higashi,0000,0000,0000,,Just three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.93,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wanna come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.37,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a bit cramped, \Nbut I'm sure we can make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.25,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to hide your displeasure, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.42,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.76,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Could we stop by the school first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.97,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.58,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a spare \Ntracksuit in his club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.14,sign_3645_34_Telepathy_Club,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H53514A&\c&H13140D&}Telepathy Club
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.14,sign_3645_35_Body_Improvement,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2E2B22&\3c&H89827A&}Body Improvement Club
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.06,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:03.02,Italics,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could borrow one for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:04.52,sign_23031_243_Body_improvement,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Body improvement
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:04.52,sign_23031_244_Lower_body_stren,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lower body\Nstrengthening month!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.52,Italics,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do it without asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.52,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Tracksuit thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.94,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.67,Italics,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,My heart just stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.86,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:18.17,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to get some dumbbells, \Nand you sure gave me a scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.12,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... You scared us pretty good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:24.83,sign_23524_249_Put_on_the_muscl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx15\clip(m 172 123 l 258 123 256 120 258 116 256 111 258 110 257 102 257 100 256 96 261 89 261 81 404 81 405 86 405 91 404 97 405 106 401 110 404 114 402 118 402 120 550 124 551 25 168 26)}Put on the muscle! Burn the fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.86,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the situation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.83,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.67,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:34.39,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Why's everyone from\Nthe Body Improvement Club here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.89,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.76,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,The Body Improvement Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.98,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,will now begin a three-day four-night \Nstrengthening hell training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.23,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.48,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,We should always help\Neach other out when in need!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.44,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're really tired—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.82,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you want to sleep on a giant futon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.28,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, a small one will do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.24,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,We have enough room for all \Nof you at my granny's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.53,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,You have to procure and make your own food,\N so it'll be excellent training!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.95,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,And it's just a 90-minute jog away!\NWe'll be there in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.04,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.58,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Reigen-san, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.54,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's great. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.37,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a cab home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.65,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Body Improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.70,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fight on! Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.70,Italics,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.43,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:21.98,Main,Teru,0000,0000,0000,,I should've just gone over \Nto Reigen-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.02,Main,Saru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.70,Main,Kiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's even more confusing up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.09,Main,Inu,0000,0000,0000,,How do one of these things even grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.45,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.60,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Aliens! This is the work of aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.02,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.46,Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.96,Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The work of our beloved leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.88,Main,Tsubomi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... It looks like a vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.09,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Mob-kun was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.22,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.60,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.14,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones behind that giant plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.87,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.77,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking if we were \Ndirectly involved, then no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.60,Main,Asahi,0000,0000,0000,,We basically were, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.15,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.48,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.61,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:17.49,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm going to stop coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.95,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki-san? But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.96,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes well with your research
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:26.29,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,and you actually develop the technology\Nto make espers out of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.92,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,we might get more espers\Nwho misuse their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.74,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,So I think you should just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.39,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.34,Main,Glasses 1,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.95,Main,Glasses 2,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually not that impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.31,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,Kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.31,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.52,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop using you for research!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.26,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest, I'm just having fun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.69,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,spending time with you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:01.12,Main,Mits,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind coming by once \Nin a while as friends, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.83,Main,Koyama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:07.08,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,The organization is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.47,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously going to have \Nto find another way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.36,Main,Koyama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:15.81,Main,Koyama,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the scars on my face are gone, \Nmaybe I'll start up a ramen shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:18.11,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,The hospitality industry is not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.76,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Just put your body to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.85,Main,Koyama,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Sakurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.42,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,I have an interview at a convenience \Nstore the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.51,Main,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're going to ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:31.19,Main,Mu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm considering asking Master Reigen \Nif I can study under him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.44,Main,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. You're really not a people person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:37.40,Main,Little,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. You're kinda dreary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.34,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The government has determined that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:47.92,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,this is the work of\Na delusional criminal organization, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.53,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you turned yourself in\Nafter being defeated by a civilian esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.04,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:57.50,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Man, where does that leave us pros?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.47,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.25,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal circumstances,\Nhe'd be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:08.48,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a chance he'll be kept alive\Nas a research subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.60,Italics,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he have to say that to his son?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.29,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not my call to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.04,Main,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:18.61,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.14,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Serizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:24.32,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I never actually considered \Nyou all my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.42,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:31.02,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Because you lack self-confidence, \Nothers will find you easy to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.98,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.46,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:40.59,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to see your mother again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:44.00,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,but my pride severed that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.46,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:47.47,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.11,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,I see Mom every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:54.19,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,She's always asking me how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:59.15,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've stopped you \Nbefore she found out what you'd become.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:02.69,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,When I called her this morning, \Nshe said she'd come see you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.57,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you dare think this is all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:10.79,Main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,You still need to get an earful from Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:26.68,Italics,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,"People need other people," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.14,sign_30874_351_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,248)}Spirits {\3c&HEAEEE9&}and Such Consultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:33.10,Main,Dimple,0000,0000,0000,,What? It was just a short circuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:36.15,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, a mouse bit into some wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:37.94,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, the fire insurance kicked in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.58,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,so we get a fresh start at a new office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:45.24,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure looks bland right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.32,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob, do your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.20,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.08,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,The hole in my uniform... I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:03.11,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'd put the broccoli seeds in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.77,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Broccoli?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:06.68,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,The seeds from back the—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:10.97,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.06,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you mean that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.51,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Welp. Let's just forget we ever saw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:21.91,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,But man, he sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.84,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:29.41,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.93,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the other day, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:33.91,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,A suit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:35.87,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:39.83,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Reigen-san made me \Nan offer after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:43.05,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,He said that there was something \Nthat even I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:47.51,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the least I can do after\Nmy organization caused everyone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:54.81,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to make a better tomorrow, \Nso this is perfect for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:57.27,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:01.25,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,My client will be here soon, \Nbut before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:01.98,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:04.58,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have to \Ndo something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:05.99,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:09.74,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.45,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,He looks so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:16.19,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he at least {\i1}looks{\i0} like\Nhe can pull off customer service now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:20.67,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,C-Customer service?! Wh-What should \NI do when a customer shows up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:22.32,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do at your last job?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:26.84,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,My orders were to smack them with\Nmy umbrella if I sensed any hostility...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.21,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:30.54,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, things aren't that different here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:32.29,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything else \Nyou don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:33.80,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,go ahead and ask your senior there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.06,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,Senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.37,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Mob, you show him the ropes \Nwhile he's still in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:39.99,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:44.23,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to work with you,\NKageyama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.25,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's... a pleasure \Nto work with you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:53.20,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? \NNow I'm getting nervous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:58.20,sign_30874_351_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\q2\3c&H8D7B75&\frz274.3\move(372,100,372,213)}Spirits {\3c&HEAEEE9&}and Such Consultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:55.55,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:23:58.20,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello there! Sorry about the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:24:00.26,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a seat right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:02.01,Main,Reigen,0000,0000,0000,,Serizawa, get our guest some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:06.22,Main,Seri,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tea? I-I'm sorry,\NI've never made tea before...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:07.47,Main,Dimp,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed.
